des:
Maybe you need a positive thought, or a little boost to change your mindset. Anna's journey to a happier life is here to help you get that extra push you need. As a life coach I will share with you daily quotes, tips to change your thoughts, book recommendations, and a little bit of humor sometimes. Check back everyday for a little bit of inspiration!

Listen to daily updates from Anna's journey to a happier life:
Start by saying "Alexa, start Anna's Journey". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
